functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

msg.content: List the 5 largest automotive manufacturers by production volume in 2010 and provide the year each company was founded.
List the 5 largest automotive manufacturers by production volume in 2010 and provide the year each company was founded.

Here are the five largest automotive manufacturers by production volume in 2010, along with their founding years:

1. Toyota Motor Corporation (1937)
2. General Motors (1908)
3. Volkswagen Group (1937)
4. Hyundai Motor Group (1967)
5. Ford Motor Company (1903)

Note that the rankings may vary depending on the specific criteria and data sources used for determining production volume. These rankings are based on global vehicle production statistics from 2010.
